Arguments

e1

is an object of class antsImage.
e2

is an object of class antsImage.

Examples


img01 <- as.antsImage(array(1:64, c(4,4,4,1)))
img02 <- as.antsImage(array(64:1, c(4,4,4,1)))
is.antsImage(img01 + img02)
#> [1] TRUE
is.antsImage(sqrt(2) * img01)
#> [1] TRUE
is.antsImage(img02 / pi)
#> [1] TRUE
